## Introduction:

Skincare products have gained popularity to help alleviate skin problems recently, such as skin problems namely acne, sunburn, and pimple brought by the humid weather. However, a lot of people have difficulty choosing the best skincare products for their skin type. The purpose of this project is to establish a simple and efficient online web application for identifying skin types and giving recommendations on skincare product selection. The raw data came from a survey conducted by a company that specializes in AI skin technology. 

## Beneficial of the product:

Young segment (teenagers) or adult woman but not limited to male as well.


