## Questions:

1. What skin problems are most common in the Malaysian population?
2. What factors do people pay more attention to when buying skin care products?
3. How does this web application assist in skincare product selection?

</style>

## Obejectives:

1. to conduct exploratory data analysis and visualize the result.
2. to conduct exploratory data analysis and interpret the result.
3. to build a prediction model and provide feasible recommendations to users.


