## conclusion:
<li> Random Forest Model obtained a high accuracy in predicting the consumption level of customers. Thus, it can be utilized in products selection, which means we can use the survey to group the customers and forecast their purchasing capability in the future. However, this app also has some certain limitations, for instance, the small sample size. Therefore, future improvement need to be considered in face of the challenges and issues at hand.
